{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC11_ELI_120.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Sophie. Hehe, you're as energetic as usual. Are you out for a walk?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, kind of. What are you doing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I'm organizing the bookshelves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "That reminds me, the bookshelves in here are always really neat and organized."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Of course they are. It would be a big problem if my customers had a hard time searching for books."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... I guess if you have this many books, it would be hard to remember where every book is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You should learn a thing or two from Elise, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Plachta. Welcome."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "P-Plachta!? Why are you here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I wanted to read a new book, so I came to browse."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "By the way, according to Plachta, it sounds like your atelier is still unorganized...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Things are scattered everywhere. There isn't even room to walk around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Uu... Stop it, Plachta... Don't say anymore..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh dear. You need to keep it clean, okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x51,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But... I'm not good at organizing things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Do you have any tricks, Elise?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. I don't have anything that could be called a trick."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I organize the books by criteria like size and genre, and place bookends between them. That's all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "...That's simpler than I thought."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's right. I'm not doing anything special."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "The other thing is to pay close attention, and clean up every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Uu... That's the worst part..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "If you make organizing a daily routine, it'll get much easier."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "You should do your best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I'll try..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "First, you need to buy some shelves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "You don't even have shelves...?"
        }
    ]
}